# installation
$ npm install -g @ionic/cli
$ ionic start myApp tabs
  tabs: blank, tabs, side menu
  you can also: --type=angular --capacitor
  capacitor: includes camera api? o_O

$ npm install @ionic/pwa-elements (?)
   import { defineCustomElements } from '@ionic/pwa-elements/loader';

   // Call the element loader after the platform has been bootstrapped
   defineCustomElements(window);

$ ionic serve

$ npm install native-run cordova-res
  native-run: to run native binaries on devices and simulators/emulators
  cordova-res: generate native app icons and splash screens o_O